<li>Like YhiF , GadE ( YhiE ) has a potential helix -- turn -- helix DNA-binding motif .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=14702398" target="_blank">14702398</a>]<br></li>
